OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Ffine end to the day and staying dry
OL,7,Fand mainly clear overnight. Some low
OL,8,Fcloud possibly forming around the
OL,9,FNorth Coast, or the odd fog patch
OL,10,Finland.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FAny low cloud soon clearing
OL,13,Fduring the morning with bright and
OL,14,Fsunny spells developing. Temperatures
OL,15,Fdown a bit, but still warm or very
OL,16,Fwarm in any sunshine. Light
OL,17,Fnorthwesterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
